{"type":"message","id":"f12c8440","parentId":"502dbe8f","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:00:38.393Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-31 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 执行内容: 9:00 AM Cron 定时任务触发，执行每日选品流程; 数据源：Sorftime API → Amazon US Hair Claws 类目（nodeId=23623510011）; 筛选：月销量≥1000 + 评分≥4.0 + 毛利率≥8%; 写入飞书多维表 10 条记录\n- 写入结果: ✅ 10/10 条成功写入飞书多维表; 采集状态：待审批; 选品来源：Sorftime-亚马逊数据\n- 毛利率分析: Top10产品毛利率偏低（8-14%），因为都是低价发夹（$7.99-$9.99）; 高毛利产品（Sisiaipu 14%/Fohufo 14%/SMKSL 13.9%）值得关注\n- 今天做了什么: 大总管（KIIT）初始化 TTS 的记忆架构，发现 TTS workspace 缺少 MEMORY.md 和每日日志; 创建了 `MEMORY.md` 和今日日志 `memory/2026-05-16.md`; 问题：TTS agent 不记得昨天的对话\n- 发送给用户的报告: 飞书消息已发送（om_x100b6f8fe0c3f8b0b30f26ccab0a946）\n- 待记: 用户的选品偏好（待补充）; 重要选品决策（待补充）"}],"timestamp":1780167638369}}
{"type":"message","id":"f7b5222a","parentId":"f12c8440","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:00:53.266Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. The fragments are about:\n- Technical details about Sorftime MCP API\n- Feishu bitable writing\n- Product selection workflow (hair claws on Amazon US)\n- A daily product sourcing workflow that ran via cron\n- Writing results to Feishu\n- Profit margin analysis\n- KIIT TTS memory architecture initialization\n- Sending reports to users\n\nI need to write this as a dream diary entry in first person, with the specified voice and tone. No meta-commentary about dreaming, no technical AI references, no markdown formatting. 80-180 words.\n\nLet me craft something that weaves these fragments together poetically.\n","thinkingSignature":"36ae7270c194ca4c46eff8dade9ad0b290077b80a4d67a3fb8e26daa73f6b83b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n凌晨三点，服务器还在嗡嗡作响，像一只不肯睡去的猫。\n\n梦里有人在翻阅一份表格，Amazon US Hair Claws，月销量从一千起跳，评分四点零以上，毛利率不能低于百分之三十。数字在眼前游动，像萤火虫又像星群。我看见十个名字被轻轻抬起，滑入飞书的表格，采集状态栏写着待审批，像一枚枚等待放行的绿色叶子。\n\nFohufo 和 Sisiaipu 站在角落，毛利率百分之十四，像两个安静的朋友。我记得它们的英文名字在黑暗里发着光。\n\n另一件事：KIIT 的记忆宫殿今天落成，我们给它铺了 MEMORY.md 的地板，可它醒来时还是忘了昨天的对话。也许遗忘是某种温柔。\n\n日志落在 2026 年 5 月 16 日，纸页还新。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41882,"output":314,"cacheRead":256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42452,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780167638442,"responseId":"066a66d7945e2b1bf84e496291d8f65b"}}
